  <description><![CDATA[<p>For three generations the Galvani family have run this superior and attractive hotel in Torri del Benaco. Located 500m from the main beach and 10 minutes' walk from the historic centre along the lake-side promenade, the Galvani hotel has a wide range of facilities which are blended with excellent cuisine and service to ensure that your stay will be a pleasant and relaxing experience.</p>]]></description>
